<abstract>
<t>This document proposes a method for splitting, recombining and sequencing datagrams across multiple logical data links.  This work was originally motivated by the desire to exploit multiple bearer channels in ISDN, but is equally applicable to any situation in which multiple PPP links connect two systems, including async links.  This  is accomplished by means of new PPPoptions and protocols.</t></abstract></front>

